## Deprecated

### 1. SimpleSpatialIndex
Replaced by RBushSpatialIndex for O(log n) performance. Do not use.

### 2. React hooks for animation state
`useState` and `useRef` for state that needs to be accessed in animation loops should NOT be used. Use `canvasStore` instead.

### 3. date-fns
Project migrated to d3-time for date operations (D3-MIGRATE-001).

### 4. r3f-perf
Package exists in dependencies but StatsMonitor (stats.js) is the reliable fallback used instead.

